 * Default: false

Whether to use the new decorator proposal.

By default, Builder uses the legacy decorator proposal when compiling
decorators.

When output.enableLatestDecorators is set to true, the Builder will compile with
the new decorator proposal (version 2018-09).

export default {
  output: {
    enableLatestDecorators: true,
