At build time, prevent some import dependencies from being packed into bundles
in your code, and instead fetch them externally at runtime.

For more information, please see: webpack Externals

EXAMPLE

Exclude the react-dom dependency from the build product. To get this module at
runtime, the value of react-dom will globally retrieve the ReactDOM variable.

export default {
  output: {
